snippet.title: The Light of the Darkness: Origins - Trailer
snippet.description: Dive into a captivating action RPG where you master physics-based flight mechanics, glide through haunting landscapes, and engage in intense souls-like combat. Navigate a realm between Light and Darkness as a unique hybrid warrior. Rediscover sidescroller magic and let destiny guide your journey.
